			Company Description 


			Randgold Resources Ltd. engages in the exploration and development of gold deposits in Sub-Saharan Africa. Its projects include loulo-gounkoto complex, morila gold mine, tongon gold mine, kibali gold mine, and massawa. The company was founded in August 1995 and is headquartered in St. Helier, Jersey...
		


                Randgold Resources Ltd. engages in the exploration and development of gold deposits in Sub-Saharan Africa. Its projects include loulo-gounkoto complex, morila gold mine, tongon gold mine, kibali gold mine, and massawa. The company was founded in August 1995 and is headquartered in St. Helier, Jersey.
            




